trans-unit.source: Converts an <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> values to and from instances of <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: Converte uma coleção <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> de valores <see cref="T:System.Windows.Point" /> de e para instâncias de <see cref="T:System.String" />.

trans-unit.source: The converted <xref:System.String> is a sequence of delimited <xref:System.Windows.Point> values.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <xref:System.String> é delimitada por uma sequência de <xref:System.Windows.Point> valores.

trans-unit.source: This class is only intended to be used by the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter> for serialization of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é destinada apenas a ser usado pelo <xref:System.Windows.Markup.Primitives.MarkupWriter> para a serialização de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Converters.PointIListConverter" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Converters.PointIListConverter" />.
